OL,4,G1310FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe B&B battle begins at the
OL,6,     GMayfield Hotel in Seaburn,
OL,7,     GSunderland. There's cause for
OL,8,     Gapplause when a seal makes an
OL,9,     Gappearance, but some guests get
OL,10,     Gpicky about the paintwork.
OL,11,G1345FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe B&Bers descend on Gateshead
OL,13,     Gfor the week's second visit, at
OL,14,     GSutherlands Hotel, where two
OL,15,     Gguests want revenge and are
OL,16,     Gdetermined to dig up some dirt.
